    "description": "这是一款用新怪谈演绎恐怖喜剧的文字冒险游戏。<br>本来喝着咖啡唱着歌，期待与大姐姐展开的粉红相亲，结果，相亲对象好像有点不正常，整个恋爱也变得畸形扭曲，染上了刺眼的猩红。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088190/extras/437487d011fa064e7b7fd9741e44dea9.avif?t=1730171264\" width=616 height=92 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088190/extras/94d9a4d68f10f41c5493baef882afd9f.avif?t=1730171264\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088190/extras_big/94d9a4d68f10f41c5493baef882afd9f.avif?t=1730171264 width=800 height=450 /></span><br><br><br>·与《文字规则怪谈》共享世界观，这个故事发生在恶鬼横行，怪谈遍地的地球173，作为普通人，不小心掉进坑里是很合理的，想要谈恋爱请使用正规的约会网站，而不要打开电脑上自动下载的某相亲网站。<br>·相亲的地点闹鬼的概率提升，修复了相亲对象是正常人的Bug。<br>·即使相亲对象是人也不能掉以轻心，她们也可能是将怪谈收容进体内，被恶鬼影响得神智不清的杀人魔。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088190/extras/088cd41c09ad0c78e33cebf9090c4207.avif?t=1730171264\" width=616 height=92 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088190/extras/96ca78f6858a7897c2413e94fc755e32.avif?t=1730171264\" width=616 height=355 /></span><br><br><br>·作为高强度冲浪的GG，玩家化身的主角除了胆大妄为没有任何优点，而且你还看了很多的无厘头恐怖喜剧。<br>·幸好相亲对象也不是正常人，说不定你们能对上电波。<br>·就算是恶鬼又怎么样？只要胆子大，贞子放产假。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088190/extras/6eb2ea7755f50161ec23cd96ab0fc4aa.avif?t=1730171264\" width=616 height=92 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088190/extras/d6c99a9147df1308d0694481190ed629.avif?t=1730171264\" width=616 height=347 /></span><br><br><br>·不能让她太爱你，不然她会把你吃掉。<br>·也不能让她太讨厌你，不然她会撕碎你。<br>·“我柜子动了，我不想玩了！”不行哦，你需要直面恐惧，攻破她的心房，让她爱上你，这样才能活下去。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088190/extras/b84cfed6bf89f22a32ec9fd8a94425ec.avif?t=1730171264\" width=616 height=92 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088190/extras/fd374388084ea8635b3b798c6208614e.avif?t=1730171264\" width=616 height=346 /></span><br><br>·穿梭于梦境的御姐医生，想要掌控梦魇。<br>·爱戴异种头的无头少女，渴望找回脑袋。<br>·名叫爱丽丝的诅咒人偶，想和你玩游戏。",
